OL,3,CFootball club to hold minute's silence
OL,4,Cfor academy player Amelia Aplin
OL,6,FOxford United will come together
OL,7,Ftonight to pay tribute to 15-year-old
OL,8,Facademy player Amelia Aplin, who
OL,9,Ftragically passed away after
OL,10,Fcollapsing during a match.
OL,12,FThe U's host Blackburn Rovers at the
OL,13,FKassam Stadium, where a minute's
OL,14,Fsilence will be observed prior to kick-
OL,15,Foff.
OL,17,FPlayers and coaching staff from both
OL,18,Fsides will also wear black armbands as
OL,19,Fa mark of respect for the talented
OL,20,Fyoung goalkeeper.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
