OL,3,CFootball club to hold minute's silence
OL,4,Cfor academy player Amelia Aplin
OL,6,FAmelia, a key member of the Girls'
OL,7,FAcademy, suffered a "serious medical
OL,8,Fincident" while playing against Fulham
OL,9,Fat the club's Horspath training centre
OL,10,Flast Saturday, March 7.
OL,12,FDespite the immediate efforts of
OL,13,Fmedical staff and emergency services,
OL,14,Fthe club confirmed on Sunday that she
OL,15,Fhad died.
OL,17,FThe tragedy has sent shockwaves
OL,18,Fthrough the sporting community.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
