PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773349949
OL,3,CFootball club to hold minute's silence
OL,4,Cfor academy player Amelia Aplin
OL,6,F"My heart is broken for her parents,"
OL,7,Fhe said. "It's been very sombre here
OL,8,Fand we have to make sure that we give
OL,9,FAmelia's friends and family all the
OL,10,Flove they need going through this
OL,11,Fterrible time."
OL,13,FThe club has invited supporters to
OL,14,Farrive early this evening to ensure
OL,15,Fthe silence is conducted with "the
OL,16,Fquiet reflection it deserves."
OL,18,FFans have also been encouraged to lay
OL,19,Ffloral tributes and messages at the Ox
OL,20,Fstatue, located outside the South
OL,21,FStand car park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
