PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773349949
OL,3,CFootball club to hold minute's silence
OL,4,Cfor academy player Amelia Aplin
OL,6,FIn a statement, Oxford United said:
OL,7,F"The Club would like to thank our
OL,8,Fsupporters, our visitors from
OL,9,FBlackburn Rovers and the wider
OL,10,Ffootball family for the overwhelming
OL,11,Fmessages of sympathy, support and
OL,12,Fsolidarity received over recent days.
OL,14,FThe thoughts of everyone at Oxford
OL,15,FUnited remain with Amelia's family,
OL,16,Ffriends and teammates."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
